Package edu.wpi.grip.core.operations.templated

Templates for various Operations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TemplateFactory
    Allows you to easily create Supplier<Operation> using only SocketHints and a lambda that will be run as part of the Operation.perform() method.

Package edu.wpi.grip.core.operations.templated Description

Templates for various Operations. Many of these classes contain duplicated code because there is no way to create types at runtime. The best place to start looking at this package is the TemplateFactory.
